#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Add Project Management</b>: Add the \"Carpentry project\" service to "
"track the entire quotation within a dedicated project."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tambah Manajemen Project</b>: Tambahkan layanan \"Project Tukang Kayu\" "
"untuk melacak seluruh surat penawaran dalam project khusus."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Automate Replenishment:</b> Set up reordering rules for key products so "
"you never run out of stock."
msgstr ""
"<b>Otomatiskan Pemulihan:</b> Setup peraturan pemesanan ulang untuk produk-"
"produk kunci sehingga Anda tidak pernah kehabisan stok."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Build the Quote</b>: Select a <b>quotation template</b>, add the required "
"products and any extra services. Use the <b>quote calculator</b> to price "
"each item based on the customer's specifications. The product tabs are "
"organized by their sequence on the sales lines."
msgstr ""
"<b>Bangun Surat Penawaran</b>: Pilih <b>templat surat penawaran</b>, "
"tambahkan produk-produk yang diperlukan dan layanan tambahan apa pun. "
"Gunakan <b>kalkulator surat penawaran</b> untuk menghargai setiap barang "
"berdasarkan spesifikasi pelanggan. Tab produk diatur berdasarkan urutan "
"mereka di baris penjualan."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Communicate and Understand Needs</b>: Use the <b>chatter feature</b> to "
"communicate with the client. This helps you clarify their specific "
"requirements for the project."
msgstr ""
"<b>Komunikasi dan Pahami Keperluan</b>: Gunakan <b>fitur obrolan</b> untuk "
"berkomunikasi dengan klien. Ini membantu Anda mengklarifikasi persyaratan "
"spesifik mereka untuk project."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Confirm Delivery</b>: Once you validate this operation, the products will "
"be automatically removed from your inventory, and the delivery can be "
"completed."
msgstr ""
"<b>Konfirmasi Pengiriman</b>: Setelah Anda memvalidasi operasi ini, produk-"
"produk akan secara otomatis dihapus dari inventaris Anda, dan pengiriman "
"dapat diselesaikan."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Create a Delivery Order</b>: Go to the <b>Project App</b> and create a "
"new <b>\"From WH\" (Warehouse) operation</b>. This acts as a delivery order, "
"listing all the finished products that need to be taken from your stock and "
"delivered to the customer."
msgstr ""
"<b>Buat Pesanan Pengiriman</b>: Kunjungi <b>Aplikasi Project</b> dan buat "
"<b>operasi \"Dari WH\" (Warehouse/Gudang)</b> baru. Tindakan ini bertindak "
"sebagai pesanan pengiriman, menuliskan semua produk yang selesai yang harus "
"diambil dari stok Anda dan dikirim ke pelanggan."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Create an Opportunity</b>: Click <b>\"Create\"</b> to start a new sales "
"opportunity."
msgstr ""
"<b>Buat Peluang</b>: Klik <b>\"Buat\"</b> untuk memulai peluang penjualan "
"baru."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Creating a Sales Order from the CRM</b>"
msgstr "<b>Creating a Sales Order from the CRM</b>"

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Define Lead Times:</b> Set lead times for all your products to ensure "
"accurate stock planning."
msgstr ""
"<b>Define Lead Times:</b> Set lead times for all your products to ensure "
"accurate stock planning."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Drag and drop tasks</b> to different stages for easy tracking."
msgstr "<b>Drag and drop tasks</b> to different stages for easy tracking."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Finalize Details</b>: Update the <b>delivery date</b> to ensure deadlines "
"are met and deliveries are scheduled correctly."
msgstr ""
"<b>Finalize Details</b>: Update the <b>delivery date</b> to ensure deadlines "
"are met and deliveries are scheduled correctly."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Generate a Manufacturing Order</b>: Within your project, create a new "
"<b>Manufacturing Order</b>. Add all the necessary components that will be "
"used, whether they are from your current stock or are new costs."
msgstr ""
"<b>Generate a Manufacturing Order</b>: Within your project, create a new "
"<b>Manufacturing Order</b>. Add all the necessary components that will be "
"used, whether they are from your current stock or are new costs."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Generate a Quotation</b>: Once you understand their needs, generate a "
"quotation from the opportunity."
msgstr ""
"<b>Generate a Quotation</b>: Once you understand their needs, generate a "
"quotation from the opportunity."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Implement a real-time quality check.</b> You can add quality checks for "
"specific products at critical moments in the manufacturing process. This "
"ensures that any defects are caught early, reducing waste and the cost of "
"rework."
msgstr ""
"<b>Implement a real-time quality check.</b> You can add quality checks for "
"specific products at critical moments in the manufacturing process. This "
"ensures that any defects are caught early, reducing waste and the cost of "
"rework."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Manage By-Products:</b> Use the <b>by-products</b> feature in the "
"Manufacturing app to reuse any remaining product parts after a production "
"run. This lets you track and manage leftover materials that are created "
"during production, reducing waste and improving efficiency."
msgstr ""
"<b>Manage By-Products:</b> Use the <b>by-products</b> feature in the "
"Manufacturing app to reuse any remaining product parts after a production "
"run. This lets you track and manage leftover materials that are created "
"during production, reducing waste and improving efficiency."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Manage product variations efficiently.</b> To handle different versions "
"of a product, such as a table made from various types of wood, you can use a "
"<b>product variant</b> system. This allows you to reuse the same <b>Bill of "
"Materials</b> (BOM) but with minor adjustments for different material types, "
"saving time and preventing errors in inventory management and production "
"planning."
msgstr ""
"<b>Manage product variations efficiently.</b> To handle different versions "
"of a product, such as a table made from various types of wood, you can use a "
"<b>product variant</b> system. This allows you to reuse the same <b>Bill of "
"Materials</b> (BOM) but with minor adjustments for different material types, "
"saving time and preventing errors in inventory management and production "
"planning."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Record time on specific tasks</b> (like \"External Help\"), and that time "
"will be used to calculate your project's profitability."
msgstr ""
"<b>Record time on specific tasks</b> (like \"External Help\"), and that time "
"will be used to calculate your project's profitability."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Select a Client</b>: Choose an existing customer from your list or add a "
"new one directly into the customer field."
msgstr ""
"<b>Select a Client</b>: Choose an existing customer from your list or add a "
"new one directly into the customer field."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Send the Quote</b>: Send the final quotation to the client, making sure "
"to attach any plans from your drawing software."
msgstr ""
"<b>Send the Quote</b>: Send the final quotation to the client, making sure "
"to attach any plans from your drawing software."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Use a shopfloor app.</b> If you have a growing team, a digital shopfloor "
"app can ensure that every employee receives the right information at the "
"right time. It can provide work instructions, track progress, and facilitate "
"communication, leading to smoother operations and fewer errors."
msgstr ""
"<b>Use a shopfloor app.</b> If you have a growing team, a digital shopfloor "
"app can ensure that every employee receives the right information at the "
"right time. It can provide work instructions, track progress, and facilitate "
"communication, leading to smoother operations and fewer errors."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Use the Replenishment Dashboard:</b> Get a clear overview of exactly what "
"you need to order."
msgstr ""
"<b>Use the Replenishment Dashboard:</b> Get a clear overview of exactly what "
"you need to order."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Validate Production</b>: Once you've completed the manufacturing process, "
"validate the order to finalize it."
msgstr ""
"<b>Validate Production</b>: Once you've completed the manufacturing process, "
"validate the order to finalize it."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>View a profitability dashboard</b> that gives you a clear overview of "
"your project's financial performance once you've properly configured all "
"costs from timesheets, production, and purchases.<b/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<b>View a profitability dashboard</b> that gives you a clear overview of "
"your project's financial performance once you've properly configured all "
"costs from timesheets, production, and purchases.<b/><br/>"

